metadata.name: t the moment, LI Shimin
metadata.description:
looked at LI Chenggan in shock. Li Chenggan was also a little confused at the moment. Did they not believe their words?



"Mother, it is true. If you resell it, you will make money. But Mother, my child is going to get married soon, and these chinaware are just in time. "Said Lee Seung-gan to Queen Changsun.
